Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Cancel a specific order (with reason parameter)
POST http://localhost:4004/sales/SalesOrders(d59cd470-f8ad-4c4a-8625-523653ed97ed)/SalesService.cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer changed their mind"
}

### Ship an order (with tracking info)
POST http://localhost:4004/sales/SalesOrders(d59cd470-f8ad-4c4a-8625-523653ed97ed)/SalesService.ship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "TRK-2026-ABC123",
